Package org.hms.entities

Class AbstractTableEntry

java.lang.Object
org.hms.entities.AbstractTableEntry
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
Direct Known Subclasses:
ContactInformation, DrugDispenseRequest, DrugInventoryEntry, DrugReplenishRequest, MedicalEntry, PatientParticulars, Staff
public abstract class AbstractTableEntry extends Object implements Serializable
Abstract base class for table entries in the Hospital Management System (HMS).

This class provides common functionality for handling CSV data and managing unique identifiers for table entries.
